**Welcome to the London region website of Diabetes UK.**
The Diabetes UK London team is working from home and our office is temporarily
closed. We are all here and ready to support in any way we can and can be
contacted via email and mobiles. If you don't have our contact details and
need to reach the team or have a general inquiry, you can get in touch via
london@diabetes.org.uk and we'll respond as quickly as we can.
Our Helpline continues to be active - call 0345 123 2399 or email
helpline@diabetes.org.uk if you have any questions or concerns regarding your
diabetes or need extra support at this time.
